text:
I’m still seeing this error on my end. I can replicate it by doing the following in the cloud IDE:

1. Create a custom module
2. Add a simple menu field
3. Add that field to the HTML pane
4. Under content options, click the Edit menu button and add an external link.
The error will now show in the console. If you add a Page Link, it’s fine, but an External Link creates the error for me.
